        <detaileddescription>
<para>Called when a progress dialog needs to be displayed</para>
<para>If cancellable (psz_cancel != NULL), you can cancel this dialog by calling <ref refid="group__libvlc__dialog_1ga2a1b69794dede8eafac5185e9e25a797" kindref="member">libvlc_dialog_dismiss()</ref></para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>to receive this callback, <ref refid="structlibvlc__dialog__cbs_1a764cbd7b1dba54ad499eded294344ce3" kindref="member">libvlc_dialog_cbs.pf_cancel</ref> and <ref refid="structlibvlc__dialog__cbs_1a501972b08256aac72d62149c31ff0174" kindref="member">libvlc_dialog_cbs.pf_update_progress</ref> should not be NULL.</para>
</simplesect>
